title: Pur Minerals 4 in 1 Pressed Mineral Makeup Foundation With SPF 15, Blush Medium
description: Pur Minerals 4-in-1 Pressed Mineral Makeup SPF 15 combines all of the benefits of a concealer, powder, foundation and sun protection to perfect and protect your complexion. Formulated with vitamin E, it nourishes and hydrates to promote healthy skin and a long-lasting, comfortable wear. Silica absorbs excess oil while organic shea butter conditions to soften and smooth, delivering a flawless, natural-looking finish and silky feel. Blush Medium is ideal for medium skin tones with pink undertones.

title: Prtty Peaushun Skin Tight Body Lotion-Dark-8 oz
description: Look great in your birthday suit with Pretty Peaushun Skin Tight Body Lotion, created by celebrity makeup artist Bethany Karlyn. Subtle light reflecting particles in a natural emollient base give the skin a gorgeous, flattering glow. Radiance conceals minor imperfections and enhances definition to create a sexy, slimmering silhouette infused with an innovative blend of natural plant extracts to lift, firm, tighten, and diminish the appearance of cellulite, stretch marks, and varicose veins, as well as minimizing bruising and sore muscles.
